How to run ?
Developement environment -    npm run dev
Production environment   -    npm run start


If you are a developer, follow these steps

install docker in your system

Build the docker image using the command
    docker build -t cybervault .
Run the docker image in interactive mode
    docker run cybervault

Test the backend service.

How to log?
User the Logger class in the utils to log anything in the terminal.

How to throw errors?
use the custom error class in utils and the middleware to thow errors.


Folder structure :
The config folder contains all the configuration files 
The controllers manage all the functionalities of the api calls 
The routers are responsible for forwarding the request to the correcdt controllers 

